Sentece: The supernatant was injected in an HPLC system comprising a Waters Symmetry NH(2) column, a mobile phase of acetonitrile/water (95/5, v/v), a flow rate of 1.0 mL/min, at 220 nm.
Title: Development and validation of a rapid method for the detection of latrunculol A in plasma.
